OL,3,CProgramme listings for SUN 29 MAR
OL,4,G0010FMud Mountain Haulers
OL,5,     GThe Glovers fight a harsh winter
OL,6,     Gon the highway while low bedding
OL,7,     Gtheir 45-tonne winch to Erie
OL,8,     GMountain. On Gollen, Craig's exit
OL,9,     Gplan faces delays from breakdowns
OL,10,     Gand a block collision.
OL,11,G0110FMud Mountain Haulers
OL,12,     GCraig and the crew return home to
OL,13,     Glog a local block, but Kylee
OL,14,     Gdiscovers its road is just as
OL,15,     Gtreacherous as Gollen. Heavy snow
OL,16,     Gburies Brent's plan to haul logs
OL,17,     Gfrom one of his blocks.
