OL,4,G0205FMud Mountain Haulers
OL,5,     GCraig's crew return to camp to
OL,6,     Glog Saddle Ridge, but boulders
OL,7,     Gmake the block nearly impossible.
OL,8,     GThe Glovers' winch spews thick
OL,9,     Gwhite smoke, and bad news arrives
OL,10,     Gfrom the government.
OL,11,G0305FMud Mountain Haulers
OL,12,     G...Skill. A million dollars'
OL,13,     Gworth of timber could be stranded
OL,14,     Gunless Craig works out a plan.
OL,15,     GBrent is weeks behind in logging
OL,16,     Gand narrowly avoids disaster
OL,17,     Gwhile uprooting a giant tree.
